{% extends "base.html.twig" %}

{% block title %}ph | summary
{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
	<div class="flex justify-center">

		<div class="flex flex-col justify-center gap-12 xl:gap-6 xl:w-[900px] w-[90vw] shadow-2xl p-10 xl:mt-0 mt-20 xl:mb-0 mb-32">


			<div>
				<p class="poppins-medium text-4xl xl:text-2xl">
					Thanks for placing your order! ðŸ˜ŠðŸŽ‰
				</p>
				<p class="poppins-light text-3xl  xl:text-lg xl:leading-6 mt-6">
					Just kidding! This is a placeholder shop, created for learning purposes with
					<span class="font-bold">Symfony PHP, Twig</span>. Implementing a real webshop is a much bigger undertaking. It would involve integrating a database and its schema (e.g. products, orders, order_details, user_data), adding financial infrastructure (e.g. Stripe, PayPal), validating forms, and much more.


